{"tid":1826013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新年隱藏活動 建議] 連儂違泊牆","createTime":"2020-01-15T20:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T09:14:08.000Z","uid":41245,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f1b562cafbc34cdfca8947eea6ff8883c27fd884","tid":1826013,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T20:22:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">此post純私怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n有鑑於以往新年係經常性有違泊問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">搞到搵位泊車鬼咁麻煩</span></span><br />\n而且執法部門係慣性包庇唔嚴查<br />\n我今年就要叫晒全世界用連儂貼撚滿你架車！順便做埋文宣，新年人流暢旺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要每人去拜年都拎定幾張文宣或者memo紙，一見違泊就輕輕貼一張（記住唔係玩批鬥，係提醒下違泊阻街啫，唔洗太過火，一兩張夠）<br />\n噉希望可以減少違泊問題，而且減少街道上車輛，推廣善用公共交通工具（黨鐵除外），從而改善空氣質素同路面交通擠塞問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsor半夜醒咗有靈感<br />\n冇人理就晏啲再開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家有個安全嘅新年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf1ec2b6f5b48abfcebe817743d24cacf66f457","tid":1826013,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T23:22:45.000Z","msg":"有無識法律既手足解答到：<br />\n<br />\n如果將文宣好似炒牌咁，純粹攝係車頭唔痴<br />\n其實係咪就算比車cam影到都唔犯法？"},{"pid":"e978e2e0cf9f2ef36a4d053f0774861dd745725b","tid":1826013,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T23:27:17.000Z","msg":"（新方向）如何令垂死的文宣活動起死回生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1826045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1826045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3bdd3e642f9ae26fc7c62504be851aa5f86c1575","tid":1826013,"uid":28244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T23:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實唔阻人幾好 香港停車場租金衰過租樓 <br />\n有升冇跌 揸車搵食個D緊係泊街啦<img src=\"/assets/face